name: Transition
description:
collaborate with ASTERASPACE & APLUS

Responding to Lucy enigma's song "Transition", recorded at the end of 2019 at Kanawa Record Yogyakarta and assisted by Studio Engineer by Kemal Akbar. Guitar, Bass, Key Instruments by Anggi, Mixing & Mastering by Aloysiusnitia.

 Believing in "we're just in time" as well as single transitions letting go of the right timing, learning to accept all the good and bad within yourself and living a life that truly is all the art of living is about and doing good.
